column1: Daily Weather Observations for Casterton, Victoria for March 2016
Prepared at 13:03 GMT on Thursday 14 April 2016   IDCJDW3012.201603
Most observations from Casterton, pressure taken from Hamilton.
Hamilton Airport is several kilometres southeast of Casterton, so the pressures will sometimes be markedly different.
Temperature, humidity, wind and rainfall observations are from Casterton {station 090182}
Evaporation and sunshine observations are from Mount Gambier Aero {station 026021}
Pressure observations are from Hamilton Airport {station 090173}
